cast.overview: A high school basketball player’s life turns upside down after free-falling into the harrowing world of drug addiction.
cast.title: The Basketball Diaries

cast.overview: Two FBI agent brothers, Marcus and Kevin Copeland, accidentally foil a drug bust. To avoid being fired they accept a mission escorting a pair of socialites to the Hamptons--but when the girls are disfigured in a car accident, they refuse to go. Left without options, Marcus and Kevin decide to pose as the sisters, transforming themselves from black men into rich white women.
cast.title: White Chicks

details.biography:
From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia.

Brittany Ann Daniel (born March 17, 1976, height 5' 7" (1,70 m)) is an American television and film actress. She is the twin sister of actress and photographer Cynthia Daniel. She is best known for her portrayal of Kelly Pitts on the CW/BET comedy-drama series The Game, and Candice in the 2010 science fiction film Skyline, and for her role as Jessica Wakefield on the 1990's teen show Sweet Valley High.
